 R←Test_HTML_002(stopFlag batchFlag);⎕TRAP;md;ns
⍝ Test <!-- tags in all flavours.
 ⎕TRAP←(999 'C' '. ⍝ Deliberate error')(0 'N')
 R←T._Failed

⍝ Not an HTML block (leading empty line missing)
