 ns←##.MarkAPL.Init''md
 ns←##.MarkAPL.Process ns
 →T.PassesIf(⊂'<p>This is a para. &lt;!–comment–&gt;</p>')∊ns.html

⍝ Not an HTML block (both empty lines are missing)
