 ns←##.MarkAPL.Init''md
 ns←##.MarkAPL.Process ns
 →T.PassesIf(,⊂'<p>This is a para. &lt;!–comment–&gt; Another para</p>')≡ns.html

⍝ From here we have real HTML blocks
